text: eya keban̆du varṇayaka eḷadenaka dæyi apa ṭa pæhædili karana men num̆ba gē paramādhipatigen apa venuven ayæda siṭinnæyi ovuhu pævasūha. niyata vaśayen ma eya, dakinnan satuṭa ṭa pat karavana kaha pæhæti ema varṇaya da vaḍā pæhædili va pavatina eḷadenaka yæyi sæbævinma ohu pavasayi yanuven (mūsā) pævæsuvēya
